Restaurants.name: Kota Kachori
Restaurants.description: It’s early hours and Koramangala is already bustling with throngs of people rushing to work. But first, they make a detour and walk straight into Kota Kachori. Well, it’s hard not to, especially when that dhaniya chutney fragrance wafts your way. Things like kachori and jalebi sit tantalizingly on the menu, and there’s the added pleasure of watching ghevar being prepared right in front of your eyes.

TopRated.name: 1131 Bar + Kitchen
TopRated.description: Easy and Breezy. That’s 1131 for you. Kick-back with a few drinks, nibblers and peppy music while enjoying the openness of the space after a long day at work. Be it their sophisticated lounge area with fern-green leather sofas, the semi-open courtyard, or their eclectic menu, 1131 Bar + Kitchen is a restobar that has ‘something for everyone’.
